<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Wildlife Removal in <%= countyName %>, <%= stateName %> | RemoveWildlifeNow.com</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Find a licensed wildlife removal contractor in <%= countyName %>, <%= stateName %>. Get connected with a local professional for raccoon, squirrel, bat, snake removal and more.">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.removewildlifenow.com/<%= stateSlug %>/<%= toSlug(countyName) %>/">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="logo">RemoveWildlifeNow<span>.com</span></a>
      <p class="tagline">Find Local Wildlife Removal Contractors — Fast</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; <a href="/<%= stateSlug %>/"><%= stateName %></a> &rsaquo; <span><%= countyName %></span>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Wildlife Removal in <%= countyName %>, <%= stateName %></h1>
        <p>Connect with a licensed local contractor serving <%= countyName %>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-box">
          <h2>Call Your Local <%= countyName %> Wildlife Removal Expert</h2>
          <p class="llp-company-name company-name" style="display:none;"></p>
          <p class="cta-sub">Licensed, insured, and local. Available for same-day and emergency service.</p>
          <div class="phone-wrap">
            <a class="llp-phone phone-cta" href="#">Call for Availability</a>
          </div>
          <p class="cta-note">Serving all of <%= countyName %>, <%= stateName %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="county-content">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Wildlife Removal Services in <%= countyName %></h2>
        <p>Homeowners in <%= countyName %>, <%= stateName %> face wildlife intrusions year-round. Raccoons, squirrels, bats, and snakes are among the most common problems — often entering through damaged soffits, vents, and rooflines. A local contractor who knows <%= countyName %> can identify entry points, remove animals humanely, and seal the structure to prevent return visits.</p>

        <h3>Services Available in <%= countyName %></h3>
        <ul class="services-list">
          <li>Raccoon removal and attic cleanup</li>
          <li>Squirrel trapping and exclusion</li>
          <li>Bat colony removal and exclusion</li>
          <li>Snake identification and removal</li>
          <li>Groundhog and mole control</li>
          <li>Bird deterrent and exclusion</li>
          <li>Dead animal removal</li>
          <li>Wildlife damage repair</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Why Hire a Local <%= countyName %> Contractor?</h3>
        <p>Wildlife removal requires knowledge of local species, seasonal patterns, and <%= stateName %> regulations. A contractor based in <%= countyName %> has handled the exact animals common to your neighborhood and knows the fastest, most effective solutions.</p>

        <h3>What to Do Before the Contractor Arrives</h3>
        <ul class="tips-list">
          <li>Note where you've seen or heard the animal (attic, crawlspace, chimney, yard)</li>
          <li>Don't attempt to handle or block animals yourself — this can be dangerous</li>
          <li>Keep pets and children away from the affected area</li>
          <li>Take photos of any damage or entry points you've found</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> RemoveWildlifeNow.com &mdash; Connecting homeowners with licensed wildlife removal professionals nationwide.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="<%- embedScript %>"></script>
</body>
</html>
